These are Puzzles for 2x2 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-1-1::.
2 different pets are kept: snake, guinea-pig
2 different brands of cigars are smoked: havana, tiparillo
1. the owner of the snake is on the left of the havana-smoker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |    2    |
| Pet   | snake  | guinea-pig |
| Cigar     | tiparillo | havana  |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-1-2::.
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: superhero, family
City: san-francisco, miami
1. the person watching family movies is on the right of the person traveling to san-francisco##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |       1       |      2       |
| Movie-Genre    | superhero      | family         |
| City   | san-francisco | miami |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-1-3::.
2 different brands of cigars are smoked: bongani, old-henry
The people's birthday is in 2 different months: november, june
1. the bongani-smoker is on the right of the person who's birthday is in june##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1     |   2    |
| Cigar   | old-henry | bongani   |
| Birthday       | june  | november |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-1-4::.
